{"tid":1416472,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"黑社會唔係最叻打劫嘅咩？","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:07:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:57.000Z","uid":119363,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b7bb56a348080f85de32812661396f0dc5c5535","tid":1416472,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:07:02.000Z","msg":"點解而家會變咗打人嘅？<br />\n<br />\n明明而家係黑社會打劫最佳時間，警察都唔得閒捉你<br />\n<br />\n但偏偏呢個時侯就無黑社會打劫<br />\n<br />\n點解呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔做啲不務正業嘅事，佢哋邊會有收入，莫非佢哋有細力人士係背後有條大水喉射住？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05249e5b13e7cbb5809d34e4014bf32eeb0e3cc9","tid":1416472,"uid":216789,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:00.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ed59ce177bbd03537e6e559d80bdfb60b9be099c","tid":1416472,"uid":119363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}